        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n@Catherine\n@Ranny\n@Eric\n\nDo we need a TSC vote to remove pnda component helm charts from OOM repo?\n\nCurrently pnda is disabled by default. Non of known use case override files enables it.\nThere is no active development and DCAE PTL (Vijay) suggested to remove it as it was just a PoC which is no longer maintained",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
