        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-10-30 15:58:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nI really am trying to  promote more inter-project collaboration in the LFN so I hate to see this go away. However, it is not worth the risk of keeping unmaintained code in ONAP. I hope some day someone will re-introduce this integration,",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
