        "timestamp": "2020-11-03 09:40:04.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nWe decided in TSC: 16/04/2020 https://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/2020+TSC+Decisions\n\"TSC approved to Disable jenkins jobs incl. SonarCloud, Daily CI + in OOM while keeping Helm Chart + document in RDT; repo not locked for the following projects in Frankfurt: Pomba, PNDA, other logging submodules and SNIRO Simulator\"\nI would also advocate to remove this chart while it is no more maintained.\nIn my opinion, no need to vote at TSC level, but just inform TSC",
